snippet.title: We Play Antichamber
snippet.description:
We Play Antichamber 

When's the last time you remember being entirely confused by a video game and loving every second of it? That's Antichamber. This indie PC title went on sale towards the end of January, and it's gathered a bit of buzz around all the oddities in brings to the world of first person puzzle solving. http://tchno.be/UYhP0Q
